reviews.review_text: beautiful if you don't see the talent and passion here,Dark Star,then listen too 105country kiks.the mesh of crowd.energy and the convergence of the minds on stage. sends us all to where Keasy wanted us to go.get on the bus.one with the stream of consciousness is what it's about.sharing that stream at precisely the moment. well there ya go. beautiful. powerful.reality. think about it . if you can. pure joy and love.
Magnifico what can you say about schoeps some of the most capable of reproducing the room. Very nice boy!
